What do I need to measure?

87
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:25,920
Do I need to do anything differently?

88
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:29,620
How will I use feedback that has been given to me?

89
00:04:29,620 --> 00:04:32,160
How do I give appropriate feedback?

90
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:37,660
And, do I understand the project management journey?

91
